{
  "stem": "12491.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean ?] [? hired-- ?] ordered some Luftwaffe or air-- air force personnel to have-- to keep guard overnight in front of the entrance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] whether we-- whether we went back to ghetto or whether we-- this was it, we were stuck there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the most difficult thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things were changing so rapidly, and thoughts were changing so rapidly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The situation was-- was changing so rapidly that your thinking was not-- never at the past.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You was-- always you were thinking of what is ahead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was one situation worthwhile explaining while I was working at the airport and still living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While I was working at the airport, I was assigned to a shop which was repairing fur coats for the German flyers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of these fur coats were torn beyond repair, and I was allowed to cut into pieces and use them to repair others, as well as have some material left.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German officers at the airport, the Luftwaffe officers, very quickly realized that I can do something for them, and I did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned how to make slippers out of fur, and gloves-- and also gloves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I made slippers and gloves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They weren't gloves with five fingers, was like-- how would you call those which have one--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mittens.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right, like mittens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were coming every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want two pairs of mittens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going on a-- on a furlough, and I want to have mittens for my wife or my daughter, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I was busy all the time making mittens that I-- I wasn't fixing furs anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't interested in the furs.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
